DeskTopSize 1x1
ClickTime 250
ColormapFocus FollowsFocus
DefaultColors black grey80
HilightColor black SteelBlue3
TitleStyle LeftJustified Height 20
TitleStyle ActiveUp Solid SteelBlue3 -- Flat
TitleStyle Inactive Solid grey65 -- Flat
ButtonStyle All -- Flat
BorderStyle Simple -- NoInset

MenuStyle * FVWM, Foreground black, Background grey82, Greyed grey55
MenuStyle * HilightBack grey72, ActiveFore black, Hilight3DOff
MenuStyle * PopupOffset 0 100, TitleWarpOff, SeparatorsShort
MenuStyle * MenuFace Solid grey82

Style "*" Color black/grey75, BorderWidth 4, HandleWidth 4
Style "*" IconBox -80x200-1-1, IconFill bottom right
Style "xterm" Color black/grey78

AddToMenu WindowOps "Window Ops" Title
+ "Xterm" Exec exec xterm
+ "Chrome" Exec exec /usr/local/bin/chrome
+ "Restart FVWM" Restart
+ "Quit Session" Quit

Mouse 1 R A Menu WindowOps Nop
Mouse 1 F N Resize
Mouse 1 A 4 Move
Mouse 3 A 4 Resize

Key Return A M Exec exec xterm
Key Tab A M WindowList "Prev FlipFocus"
Key Tab A 4 Desk 1 0 0 3
